reviewText: Cheaply made movie and terrible acting! I don't care how bored I am, I will not watch it again! Buy at your own risk... consider yourself warned!
Interesting story.  Gorilla-style independent film making at it's best.
If someone would have taken a rope and hung me, they would have put me out of my misery quicker.  I find this movie should be used as a tool to  torture our enemies.
